story.text: The roller coaster of emotional discord in my life has led me to question all relationships. This has led to a dearth of truly meaningful relationships, I think. I have thousands of friends. Very few people who are dear. I want to rebound from this tragedy to find true friends. Yet, I know not how to find them.
